snippet.title: Announcement Trailer - Fiend Legion CCG
snippet.description:
Fiend Legion combines tactical CCG elements with classic turn-based strategy that rewards quick-thinking and decisiveness.

Set in a dark-fantasy world full of monsters and myths, FL will bring players full online multiplayer, as well as a story-driven single player campaign with challenging game-boards that change with each level's environment.
